        "title: \"Replication of Card and Krueger (1994)\"\n",
        "subtitle: \"Minimum Wages and Employment: A Case Study of the Fast-Food Industry in New Jersey and Pennsylvania\"\n",
        "author: \"Alina Markova\"\n",
